snippet.title: The most ridiculous & funniest ANIMAL videos #3 - Funny animal compilation - Watch & laugh!
snippet.description:
Animals are so funny, cute and awesome! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, goats, bears, horses, turtles... behave, play, sleep and snore, fail,...! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
